1 STATE OF OKLAHOMA
2 2nd Session of the 60th Legislature (2026)
3 HOUSE BILL 3927 By: Pfeiffer
4
5
6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to education; creating the Schools
Reform Act of 2026; providing for noncodification;
8 and providing an effective date.
9
10 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
11 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
12 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
13 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Schools Reform
14 Act of 2026".
15 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
